- **PCA variance preserved**: RNA {{ "%.1f" | format(metrics.pca_variance_preserved.gdsc2_train_rna * 100) }}%
  (GDSC2 train) / {{ "%.1f" | format(metrics.pca_variance_preserved.prism_test_rna * 100) }}%
  (PRISM test), mutations {{ "%.1f" | format(metrics.pca_variance_preserved.gdsc2_train_mut * 100) }}%
  / {{ "%.1f" | format(metrics.pca_variance_preserved.prism_test_mut * 100) }}%

